protected_spaces_details.description: Provision for children and young people

description: The erection of seven mixed-use buildings A, B1, B2, B3, C, D and E (a 'link' building situated between block B1 and D) ranging in height from 8 to 42 storeys. New buildings to comprise: 901 residential units (Class C3); 1,104 sqm (GIA) of ground-floor mixed-use (Use Class B1/ A1/ A2/ A3/ A4/ D1); a 1,049 sqm (GEA) 'leisure box' (Use Class D2); plant and storage accommodation, including a single basement to provide vehicle and cycle parking, servicing and plant areas; new vehicle and pedestrian accesses and new public amenity spaces and landscaping. [AMENDED PROPOSALS]
